  "text": "HomeCareersTune in live this Thursday, Jan. 30 to ask the academic trailblazer all your fashion education questions.Janelle here. I'm so excited to share that I'll be joining Dr. Joyce Brown, president of the Fashion Institute of Technology (FIT), on The Fashionista Network. But here's the best part: I want you to join me! It's your opportunity to interact live with us, ask questions and be a part of the show.We'll discuss Dr. Brown's decades-long tenure as FIT's first woman and Black president, how she's implemented DEI and sustainability initiatives at the school, the current state of fashion education and more.This conversation will be hosted on The Fashionista Network powered by interactive media platform Fireside, and you'll get the chance to participate and join the stage with video to ask questions directly. Learn more about The Fashionista Network here.Scroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesYou don't want to miss this show on Thursday, Jan. 30 at 11:30 a.m. PT/2:30 p.m. ET. Sign up for free access now (and don't forget to become a member to access all of our members-only shows and perks as well).Homepage Photo: Bennett Raglin/Getty Images for FITTune into The Fashionista Network to join the conversation with fashion and beauty industry leaders. Sign up here.Subscribe to Our Newsletter",
